Two issues:

1. OLD TAP SYNTAX - Uses deprecated `~source -> dest` instead of `~tap(source -> dest)`
   The logger.kz uses:
     ~input:compute -> *
   Should be:
     ~tap(input:compute -> *)

2. REQUIRES INTERCEPTOR FEATURE - Same as 310_001, attempts pass-through:
   | done |> result { result: r }

Once interceptors are implemented and syntax is updated, this test
should work. See 365_INTERCEPTORS/SPEC.md for interceptor design.
